comments: Ayton (PHX) makes contact with the ball as simultaneous marginal contact occurs with Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) right arm. Warren (PHX) is moving forward toward Caldwell-Pope at the same time and marginal contact occurs with Caldwell-Pope's back as he secures the ball.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Shamet's (PHX) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Durant (PHX) contests the put-back attempt and marginal contact occurs with Gordon's (DEN) right arm as Gordon finishes at the rim.
Gordon (DEN) makes contact with the ball after it exits the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Ayton (PHX) is firming up when he makes contact with Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) side. The contact is still within the frame of Ayton's body during the pick.
As Caldwell-Pope (DEN) loses his balance from the preceding contact, he falls forward toward Booker (PHX) and marginal contact occurs with Booker's lower body along the sideline.
Gordon (DEN) initiates contact with Durant's (PHX) right arm and affects Durant's ability to bring his right hand to the ball after gathering it in his left hand.
Brown (DEN) turns slightly as he establishes himself in Shamet's (PHX) path and he does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the pick.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Shamet's (PHX) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Shamet (PHX) legally contests Murray's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) briefly has his arm around Booker's (PHX) midsection before correcting.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) brings his right arm up to defend the pass attempt and marginal contact occurs with Booker's (PHX) right arm after he releases it.
Booker (PHX) brings his right hand toward Murray's (DEN) left hip and marginal contact occurs as the long rebound falls overhead.
Ayton (PHX) and Gordon (DEN) come together at the same spot and marginal side-to-side contact occurs as they each pursue the loose ball.

Replay review of the out of bounds call pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Ayton (PHX) touches the ball last before going out of bounds and the call on the floor was overturned to Denver's ball.
Booker (PHX) briefly has his hands on Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) sides before disengaging.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) establishes himself in Ayton's (PHX) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Shamet (PHX) immediately slides his arms off of Jokic's (DEN) upper body and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Shamet's (PHX) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Jokic (DEN) loses control of the ball on his own prior to incidental body contact being made by Shamet (PHX).
After the ball becomes loose, Murray (DEN) falls to the ground and makes incidental contact with Ayton (PHX) leg on the play.
Both Ayton (PHX) and Jokic (DEN) are in contact with the ball when PHX signals for a timeout.  A held ball is correctly whistled.
Ayton (PHX) grabs and holds down Jokic's (DEN) right shoulder, affecting Jokic's ability to compete for the jump ball.
Porter Jr. (DEN) commits a take foul on Warren (PHX).
Warren (PHX) avoids making contact with Jokic's (DEN) right arm and legally contests the driving shot attempt.
Durant (PHX) cleanly back-taps the ball away from Jokic (DEN) prior to incidental contact occurring.
Porter Jr. (DEN) commits a take foul on Durant (PHX).
Durant (PHX) and Murray (DEN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Ayton (PHX) legally contests Jokic's (DEN) layup attempt.
Porter Jr. (DEN) commits a take foul on Shamet (PHX).
Booker (PHX) brings his hand toward Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) right side and marginal contact occurs during Caldwell-Pope's driving shot attempt.
